CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A6 reads: "NAACP Life Membership - Lawrence Prattis, Grand Attorney for Prince Hall Masons of Pennsylvania, presents Grand Master A. William Hill Jr. with a life membership plaque from the NAACP, during the banquet of the Grand Lodge session, at the Hotel Penn-Sheraton."
TitMainTitle: Lawrence Prattis presenting Grand Master A. William Hill Jr. with a NAACP life membership plaque during Prince Hall Grand Lodge banquet in the Penn Sheraton hotel
